TSReportViewer
==============

Install
-------
- ```git@github.com:lucasmouilleron/TSReportViewer.git```
- Create an Apache vhost pointing to the source folder :
    - ```sudo vi /etc/apache2/vhosts.conf```
    - ```<VirtualHost *:80>
        ServerName dev.reports.turing-solutions.com
        ServerAlias dev.reports.turing-capital.com
        DocumentRoot "/PATH/TO/TSReportViewer"
    </VirtualHost>```
- Create a virtual domaine : 
    - ```sudo vi /etc/hosts```
    - ```127.0.0.1 dev.reports.turing-capital.com```

Run
---
- Debug run : http://dev.reports.turing-capital.com/index_debug.html
- Production run : 
    - Build project : 
        - ```_dev/build.sh```
        - or watch : ```_dev/watch.sh```
        - or run target "build"
    - http://dev.report.turing-capital.com
